 ('1', '5', 'en_au', '<p>We believe brands have the cultural influence and resources to change our world for the better. Big problems or small. Global or grassroots.</p>\n<p>Over the past 10 years, our team has worked in Sydney, San Francisco, London and Berlin delivering world-class design and strategy for global clients, from banks, telcos and airlines to luxury brands, fashion labels and music festivals.</p>\n<p>Evolving social values and technology are changing the way we live. Today’s consumers are demanding more than products and services. They want brands that are authentic, intelligent and ethical.</p>\n<p>Businesses have to adapt.</p>\n<p>We started Luka to use our industry experience to help those who share our worldview work towards a brighter future.</p>\n<p>If you’re a start-up, social innovator, B-corp, a for-purpose business, or simply one with the ambition to make a difference, we’d love to hear from you.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-07-05 20:51:43', '2017-07-20 17:10:14', 'cc005a74-5c9b-4d0a-923a-71bd68f32472'),
 ('2', '7', 'en_au', '<p>We craft meaningful ideas and experiences to build distinctive, memorable brands.</p><p>The things we do best are:</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-07-05 20:54:00', '2017-07-20 17:09:28', '021b9872-68fb-408d-8441-1632d6ada97e'),
 ('3', '8', 'en_au', NULL, NULL, 'Brand Creation', 'Brand Activation', '2017-07-05 20:54:00', '2017-07-20 17:09:28', '46bf1453-7b97-4422-972b-d6e74f0db819'),
 ('5', '22', 'en_au', '<p>Our team of creative activists have worked for award-winning design studios and branding agencies in Sydney, San Francisco, London and Berlin.</p><p>We have a not-so-little black book of developers, animators, photographers, film-makers, illustrators, set designers and music composers that we collaborate with.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-07-20 17:11:06', '2017-07-20 17:11:06', '86972290-cfe4-40b6-8c54-5c575249b63d'),
 ('6', '24', 'en_au', NULL, '<p>Be the change you want to see in the world</p>', NULL, NULL, '2017-07-20 17:15:27', '2017-07-20 17:36:18', '48cec6f6-4357-4c0a-96f1-f1f58ec35dc3'),
 ('7', '25', 'en_au', '<p>Chat to us about your idea, project or initiative.</p>\n<p><a href=\"mailto:hello@luka.agency\">hello@luka.agency</a></p>\n<address>Luka Agency<br />5 Woodburn Street,<br />Redfern 2016<br />Australia</address>\n<p><a href=\"mailto:hello@luka.agency\">See our portfolio</a><br /><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/luka.agency/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Follow us on Instagram</a></p><p><br /></p>\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-07-20 17:15:27', '2017-07-20 17:36:18', '03da4d41-a0e5-48b6-87a3-e509472848a6');



